<h3 local-id=3D"15a3cb5ac5b7" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-3.1Infrastruct=
ureOverview"><strong>3.1 Infrastructure Overview</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"4545ee209fbb">The architecture consists of three main layers=
:</p>
<hr local-id=3D"6bc2cff1af1d">
<h3 local-id=3D"df34a00b47b2" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-1.MonitoringLa=
yer"><strong>1. Monitoring Layer</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"aa9dc8a097f0">
<li local-id=3D"a9528ef1d311">
<p local-id=3D"6c0a24a8e660">Prometheus collects system-level metrics</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"791444253ed8">
<p local-id=3D"7adeef7a8255">Metrics include CPU usage, memory usage, and u=
ptime</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"37b0fbaadfb7">
<h3 local-id=3D"51e4b3ce33a8" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-2.AlertingLaye=
r"><strong>2. Alerting Layer</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"35f430236f84">
<li local-id=3D"205722a7e21c">
<p local-id=3D"c62e067b3509">Grafana evaluates alert rules based on thresho=
lds</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7e624d2582d">
<p local-id=3D"a1593bba658a">Alerts triggered when conditions are met (e.g.=
, high CPU usage)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"877ae1043cc2">
<h3 local-id=3D"0a61fcb2987b" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-3.Notification=
Layer"><strong>3. Notification Layer</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"1d4f2bd102d8"><strong>Alerts are routed through multiple cha=
nnels:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4498d09e4e56">
<li local-id=3D"94399e8b4132">
<p local-id=3D"b4eaede7cf61">SMTP (Postfix): Direct email delivery</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfe600097f7b">
<p local-id=3D"b62b9d033c2a">AWS SES: Cloud-based email delivery</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b7ad72526ed7">
<p local-id=3D"6d81e5d23146">AWS SNS: Message routing layer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f8a008517fa">
<p local-id=3D"340304daa9fa">AWS WorkMail: Enterprise email inbox</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"681df6cb6aaf">
<h3 local-id=3D"757308fedcdc" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-ArchitectureFl=
ow"><strong>Architecture Flow</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">Grafana=
 Alert =E2=86=92 Notification Channel =E2=86=92
    =E2=86=92 SMTP (Postfix =E2=86=92 Gmail Relay)
    =E2=86=92 AWS SES =E2=86=92 SNS =E2=86=92 Email
    =E2=86=92 AWS WorkMail =E2=86=92 SNS =E2=86=92 Email Inbox</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"cd2d3dde0645">
<h3 local-id=3D"208a52517bd7" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-3.2Environment=
s"><strong>3.2 Environments</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"eaf3f3912d8c">
<li local-id=3D"503c3bbfb3cc">
<p local-id=3D"f86813383871"><strong> </strong>A single testing environment=
 was used for this implementation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8991e9d0c175">
<p local-id=3D"cfcd3d773672">The environment includes:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e54979be0961">
<li local-id=3D"4a2f4bba0ec2">
<p local-id=3D"d20ab086d99c">Monitoring setup (Prometheus + Grafana)</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"660dff5e30dd">
<p local-id=3D"79ab94da7446">Email infrastructure setup</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"53b83fc29870">
<p local-id=3D"9601c9614397">Alert validation workflows</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"55afc10aa9d2">This setup simulates a real-world DevOps monit=
oring pipeline in a controlled environment.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"2374df94be4e">
