<hr local-id=3D"c71970e20412">
<h3 local-id=3D"ff01f0e4dee9" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-3.4Application=
Flow"><strong>3.4 Application Flow</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"25cc97edc3ba"><strong>The alerting workflow operates as foll=
ows:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ff819dfa79ed">
<li local-id=3D"9d17720f7e8d">
<p local-id=3D"aee545f45ee8"><strong>Metrics Collection:</strong><br>
 Prometheus continuously collects system metrics.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c00d023cff9a">
<p local-id=3D"0fb682d1a37b"><strong>Alert Evaluation:</strong><br><strong>=
 </strong>Grafana evaluates predefined alert rules based on metrics.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"2f8877139af2">
<p local-id=3D"2257f0b75c1c"><strong>Alert Trigger:</strong><br><strong> </=
strong>When a condition is met (e.g., CPU &gt; threshold), an alert is trig=
gered.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bf79332e2032">
<p local-id=3D"4928ca8fb097"><strong>Notification Routing:</strong><br><str=
ong> </strong>The alert is routed through one of the configured channels:</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"3c75104838c6">
<li local-id=3D"54077a9f6490">
<p local-id=3D"fcbc5b795cb1">SMTP (Postfix)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"45bb60c76955">
<p local-id=3D"304f8c79fff3">SES via SNS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"84b3820e0f0d">
<p local-id=3D"ff192a5840a8">WorkMail via SNS</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"474eeb1d849b">
<p local-id=3D"ab725e239789"><strong>Email Delivery:</strong><br><strong> <=
/strong>The alert is delivered to the user=E2=80=99s email inbox.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"83d96068d596">
<p local-id=3D"e9a155b6f3d8"><strong>User Response:</strong><br>
 The user receives the alert and takes necessary action.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"455a1db7975c">
<h2 local-id=3D"62c4142e65ce" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentP=
ractices"><strong>4. Development Practices</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"1cfaff3b1fd5" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionCont=
rol"><strong>4.1 Version Control</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"18862deae3b6">Not applicable for this implementation, as the=
 setup involves infrastructure and configuration rather than application co=
de development.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"ed3fe97ae1d1">
<h3 local-id=3D"a5b5681881e1" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousI=
ntegration"><strong>4.2 Continuous Integration</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"047de47bc02e">
<li local-id=3D"044255d9fe93">
<p local-id=3D"e742ef1bffb7"><strong> Manual configuration using: </strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"9ba72261d202">
<li local-id=3D"7fcb8fea2128">
<p local-id=3D"fa86761c6966"><strong> </strong>Grafana UI</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a614179d959a">
<p local-id=3D"55062ee8a668">AWS Console</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e544899ffe9a">
<p local-id=3D"c2e50814053b"><strong> No CI/CD pipeline implemented </stron=
g></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f8cbfbcba6a9">
<h3 local-id=3D"66cfe49e2a24" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTe=
sting"><strong>4.3 Automated Testing</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"c941725d245b"><strong>Alerts were tested using simulated sce=
narios:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bea78e7f19bb">
<li local-id=3D"35effcf28050">
<p local-id=3D"9f2f6a462fe5"><strong>High CPU Usage Alert:</strong><br>
 Triggered by increasing system load</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b32852f55c47">
<p local-id=3D"7fd215adcfb6"><strong>No Data Alert:</strong><br>
 Triggered when Prometheus metrics were unavailable</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3132da22b8c5"><strong>These tests ensured:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"cddeb9ec97fe">
<li local-id=3D"010f0a18c16c">
<p local-id=3D"6b71d6fabf16">Alert rules are functioning correctly</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aecd3883c583">
<p local-id=3D"14ca1eb44930">Notification channels are properly configured<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"fb27a8492f96">
<h3 local-id=3D"ea013d6d9dd4" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQuality=
"><strong>4.4 Code Quality</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"47fcc6aa38ac"><strong>Validation was performed based on:</st=
rong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f4ed348b7675">
<li local-id=3D"b36a4faa30dc">
<p local-id=3D"02c1f5431360"><strong> </strong>Successful email delivery ac=
ross all channels</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb2b0aea469c">
<p local-id=3D"8f8e5989d54f">Proper SMTP handshake and authentication</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e15f8e70f050">
<p local-id=3D"78920cd22ab6">Absence of errors in Postfix logs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"22310a66f915">
<p local-id=3D"8cf10f77926e">Verified alert messages in email inbox</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"ca59296cec04">
<h2 local-id=3D"014e049eefa2" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-5.Deploymentan=
dReleaseManagement"><strong>5. Deployment and Release Management</strong></=
h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"699617385714" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentS=
trategy"><strong>5.1 Deployment Strategy</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"946c8b6c4334"><strong>The deployment was carried out in sequ=
ential phases:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"011bb2738dfe">
<li local-id=3D"14d0f1ff79be">
<p local-id=3D"f923e8ffd6f1">Install and configure Postfix</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ec558f3cb15c">
<p local-id=3D"3995201b105d">Configure Grafana SMTP settings</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"31ec4fed9aa5">
<p local-id=3D"3041b6182688">Setup AWS SES and verify identity</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5a6343cf0058">
<p local-id=3D"a0b532142f1a">Create SNS topic and subscription</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73507ad34213">
<p local-id=3D"e61ccd1878f1">Setup AWS WorkMail organization and mailbox</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"e36f1dd78943">
<p local-id=3D"19586baad2bc">Integrate all services with Grafana</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1021443e94a6">
<p local-id=3D"9c0a953b43a4">Perform end-to-end testing</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"3dbe99e76337">
<h3 local-id=3D"547072da60b9" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-5.2Configurati=
onManagement"><strong>5.2 Configuration Management</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"8763c42d44b8"><strong>Configuration was managed using:</stro=
ng></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1816d22c8488">
<li local-id=3D"c3050c04930e">
<p local-id=3D"fb5fefb5fb80">Postfix configuration files (main.cf, sasl_pas=
swd)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a739fd460e2b">
<p local-id=3D"2924256b842e">Grafana configuration file (grafana.ini)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"a7b09c0e8898">
<p local-id=3D"be4019cf2547">AWS Console for SES, SNS, and WorkMail</p></li=
>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d8849bf4a80e">
<h3 local-id=3D"fff7e7b3dba6" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousD=
elivery"><strong>5.3 Continuous Delivery</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"937c2dcbbc3f"><strong>The alerting system functions as a con=
tinuous delivery mechanism, where:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d597fde7fc26">
<li local-id=3D"befed34d9bf0">
<p local-id=3D"a3a0c7508163">Alerts are continuously generated based on sys=
tem state</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c327aff75a2">
<p local-id=3D"9a9e11943370">Notifications are delivered in real-time</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e091f540173e">
<p local-id=3D"4690ecad7c60">No manual intervention is required after setup=
</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"14c710bc11e2">
<h2 local-id=3D"b7d14d62416d" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-6.Monitoringan=
dIncidentManagement"><strong>6. Monitoring and Incident Management</strong>=
</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"2d939ea7aaec" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringT=
oolsandMetrics"><strong>6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</strong></h3>
<p local-id=3D"1e091350beb8"><strong>Monitoring was implemented using:</str=
ong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"83bbc14ba57e">
<li local-id=3D"6740f272bcf7">
<p local-id=3D"742615ac5793"><strong>Prometheus: </strong>Metrics collectio=
n</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3942f2e01b0">
<p local-id=3D"13e464d802e5"><strong>Grafana: </strong>Visualization and al=
erting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d11f03e971df">
<p local-id=3D"da404abd891c"><strong>AWS Console: </strong>Infrastructure m=
onitoring</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"978abd6aff5c"><strong>Metrics Monitored:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"24f5d6aabd14">
<li local-id=3D"d08e3816aa93">
<p local-id=3D"023ef8fdb35d"><strong> </strong>CPU usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1fc3ba67f99b">
<p local-id=3D"348e1dd4da70">Memory usage</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9b5cc7efb5c7">
<p local-id=3D"b8383968b6b6">System uptime</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5cd90e4fbcc2">
<p local-id=3D"7e08979d62b9">Alert conditions</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b8516d02da1c">
<h3 local-id=3D"3c103136fc08" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-6.2Alertingand=
Notification"><strong>6.2 Alerting and Notification</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bce3bf3af695">
<li local-id=3D"46bec76286cc">
<p local-id=3D"53844cbc59af"><strong> </strong>Alerts configured in Grafana=
 using threshold-based rules</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e593a74007d2">
<p local-id=3D"60807080d9bb"><strong> Notifications sent via: </strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e4ba7f5d47a7">
<li local-id=3D"87b77107eb67">
<p local-id=3D"9f1db953f12b"><strong> </strong>SMTP</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ac96063c5f9">
<p local-id=3D"64da1f7108e1">SES</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7ec031fe9d3b">
<p local-id=3D"6d8de72a607b">WorkMail</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"16f761fab3d8">
<p local-id=3D"98eb768347a7">Real-time alert validation performed</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"01d4099afd13">
<h3 local-id=3D"0e64d9fed3e5" id=3D"Task19-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentMan=
agement"><strong>6.3 Incident Management</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0651068a0fb4">
<li local-id=3D"219b3f956fd7">
<p local-id=3D"6d3359f037d8"><strong> </strong>Alerts notify users immediat=
ely upon issue detection</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"16a7a3f3a58d">
<p local-id=3D"93da9d4320e6">Enables quick diagnosis and response</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ef76b4234971">
<p local-id=3D"e71eee2f3b67">Reduces downtime and improves system reliabili=
ty</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"34d4a3468dc5">
